title: 273.1342 ELECTRIC GENERATING PLANTS IN TACONITE TAX RELIEF AREAS.
text: For purposes of definitions of "taconite tax relief area" and "taconite assistance area" in sections 273.134, 273.1341, and related laws, the elimination of the property tax exemption for certain electric generating plants under Laws 2008, chapter 154, article 8, section 6, does not change the status of any electric generating plant qualifying as a taconite facility.
